			(property "Description" "The R1LP0108E Series is a family of low voltage 1-Mbit static RAMs organized as 131, 072-word by 8-bit, fabricated by Renesass high-performance 0. 15um CMOS and TFT technologies. The R1LP0108E Series has realized higher density, higher performance and low power consumption. The R1LP0108E Series is suitable for memory applications where a simple interfacing, battery operating and battery backup are the important design objectives. It has been packaged in 32-pin SOP, 32-pin TSOP and 32-pin sTSOP."
